list publicipaddresses  listall=true filter=id
{
  "count": 55,
  "publicipaddress": [
    {
       ....
    }
    ]
}    

## With Pagination

 list publicipaddresses  pagesize=5 page=1 listall=true filter=id
{
  "count": 5,    <--- while count has to be 55, it returns 5 which is the value of pagesize
